{"tid":2212250,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"話說幾個月前發左個夢 有關散仔強 真發夢","createTime":"2020-09-21T15:52:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T04:00:16.000Z","uid":359022,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9cc71c744c9a7e7d99d866f00c5219d32fc5a7d0","tid":2212250,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T15:52:26.000Z","msg":"個網laglag地慢慢打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9023c322fc0328814550037f9e893be4d4ff039f","tid":2212250,"uid":166308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T15:52:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58888fad27535c806df2d35c59392abf1d7a24b","tid":2212250,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:10:42.000Z","msg":"查實都唔係幾個月前，正確d黎講大約兩個月。<br />\n有一晚我夢見柒頭憎x偉，一堆散仔及一個被害者（警察）。<br />\n<br />\n雖然好努力想記得個被害者個名，但係最後因為好想追埋個夢就忘記了。淨係記得個名係三個字。<br />\n<br />\n但係個夢入面，好似不停有唔同形式嘅嘢提醒我要記得1977呢個年份<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知有無人知1977發生過咩事呢"},{"pid":"c96652f296e00ec1d4ad1989f74f9d5c09d7b7f9","tid":2212250,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:12:15.000Z","msg":"利申：未發呢個夢之前細佬無睇過1977相關嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n發完個夢先去搵下資料，既然係咁提呢個年份<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a179166a728e28bf951993d03e3ff2bffcd65b65","tid":2212250,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:13:42.000Z","msg":"有無lm 有無lm 無就唔打了<br />\n反正當時係第二度有打 費事被講馬後炮咩都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d40c8dc695294b606d8136f0ec2a3c52e51b0121","tid":2212250,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:14:54.000Z","msg":"聽晚唔lag機再續"},{"pid":"adce9af1cf233e9163663badd907b92437186a23","tid":2212250,"uid":369920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c96652f296e00ec1d4ad1989